File Structure (layout)

S3 Bucket (obtain static files of WP landing page)
- s3-bucket-name/
  - index.html
  - css/
    - styles.css
  - js/
    -scripts.css
  - images/
    - logo.png
    - background.jpg

EC2 instance (dynamic content)
- root folder
  - wp-content/
    -plugins/
    -themes/
    -uploads/
    ...etc. 
  - <other wp files>
  - php-pages/
    -login.php
    -process.php
    ...etc.

